snippet.title: ACE: Air Combat Emulator [Longplay]
snippet.description:
What do you think of this ACE: Air Combat Emulator longplay for the Commdore 64?
This is a longplay of the european version which was released in 1985.
The video will show a full walkthrough and display the gameplay.

Did you play this game or have any opinion on what you can see?
Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

Completion Criteria: Credits

Developed by: Ian Martin
Published by: Cascade Games , Spinnaker Software
Played by: Gremolin
